Package: smartcount
Title: A Toolkit for Count Regression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Xinran", "Wang", , "xinranwang@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A statistical toolkit for count regression analysis. Provides
    functions to summarize count data, fit Poisson, Quasi-Poisson, Negative
    Binomial, and Zero-Inflated regression models, assess model conditions,
    produce diagnostic plots, and interpret model output in clear terms.
